Package: linux-diagnostics
Version: 1.0.0
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-yaml, python3-subprocess
Description: Linux Diagnostics Controller Daemon
 This package provides a daemon for monitoring and diagnosing issues in Linux systems.
 It reads configuration from a YAML file and executes diagnostics based on specified anomalies.